            <Label layoutX="52.0" layoutY="50.0" prefHeight="54.0" prefWidth="851.0" text="Encapsulation allows to restrict access to certain components in the object, allows to protect members of the class from external access in order to guard against unauthorized access. Changes within class will not affect external code." wrapText="true" />
